&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Create the project:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Go P2P Development: From Basics to PubSub</title><link>https://blog.mickeyzzc.tech/en/posts/network/golang-p2p-development/</link><pubDate>Mon, 05 Jun 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.mickeyzzc.tech/en/posts/network/golang-p2p-development/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Go&amp;rsquo;s simple concurrency model and fast compilation make it a popular choice for P2P network development. go-libp2p is one of the most complete libp2p implementations and is widely used in large projects like IPFS (Kubo).&lt;/p&gt;
